    <abstract>
      <t>   This document defines a YANG data model to configure and manage IPv6
   address resolution based on IPv6 Neighbor Discovery (ND) protocol and
   other related functions, including proxy Neighbor Advertisement,
   Neighbor Unreachability Detection (NUD), and Duplicate Address
   Detection (DAD).

